tfestimators - R Interface to Estimator API in TensorFlow

This package provides a high-level interface to TensorFlow in R, using the Estimator module distributed as part of TensorFlow.

To generate and preview docs locally, run:

devtools::install_github("hadley/pkgdown")
pkgdown::build_site()
